<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA66">
<l>miṭaṟṟil viṭamuṭaiyī rummiṭaṟṟai nakki</l>
<l>miṭaṟṟil viṭaṅkoṇṭa vāṟō - miṭaṟṟakattu</l>
<l>maittā miruḷpōlum vaṇṇaṅ karitālō</l>
<l>paittāṭu nummārpiṟ pāmpu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it the way if takes the poison in [your] throat, licking at the throat</l>
<l>of you too who have poison in [your] throat, is it that is it black</l>
<l>in colour like the night that has become black inside [its] throat,</l>
<l>the snake on your chest that spreads [its] hood?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
